snippet.textDisplay: I have never in my entire life touched anything from Final Fantasy. The only time I had ever heard anything from or about it was when I played Roblox back in 2011 because many games would use Final Fantasy music. I just want to say that I now know what this is and I can tell you with absolute unequivocal certainty that this is without a doubt the most autistic, uncomfortable, disgusting, degenerate thing I have ever laid eyes upon. I have not even a shred of doubt that this is the fruit of a broken mind. I am so disappointed that this is actually considered a popular game series. Only in Japan could a series so despicable and unfortunate be birthed. Everything about the characters, plot, voice acting, and gameplay causes my blood to brew. As an American citizen, I've now made up my mind that it's my duty to seek war with Japan once more. Clearly, we did not drop enough nukes on that god forsaken archipelago. This filth absolutely needs to be destroyed and all evidence of this game series ever existing needs to be completely erased.
